	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.22]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>4 songs is twistable on good connection, good timing, and using top down view (one click on the view button, reduces lag during battle like those ANNOYING laggy AE rain spells!). i cannot do it since my connection sux, but i can do 4 wit allowing one effect to drop for a second. you'll get the timing down overtime, just keep practicing, its good to practice during downtime since theres little lag then. if you put your mind to it, anything can be accomplished&nbsp;&nbsp;=)<br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>40th Season<br>House of Wargoth<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
