	   <tr><td colspan=2>"Wisp Island" is an island between the continents of Antonica and Odus.&nbsp;&nbsp;To get there, take the boat from the Qeynos dock.  It stops at the island on the way to Erudin.  The zone is "Erud's Crossing", and you will recognize the small island from the cat people that inhabit it.<br><br>Be careful, there is no zone nearby to run to if you get in trouble.  The only way out is to take the boat to Erudin.  Also, I would highly advise against attacking anything else on the island, especially the spiders, as they gang up very quickly to help each other.<br><br>Have fun!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
