	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Best Race: I have no idea why so many people make half elf bards.&nbsp;&nbsp;The exp penalty to make a hybrid class with a hybrid race is crazy.  Make a human, no penalty and the only difference in stats is 10 less dex for 10 more str (same cha).<br><br>Where You Should Put Your Stats:  There aren't many bard songs that use charisma but some key ones do, so put about 10 points there.  If you followed what i said and made a human bard then you'll need a little more dex, maybe 5 to 10 points.  If you didn't follow what i said and made a wood elf of half elf bard put 5 to 10 points into strength.  Put your remaining points into agility.<br><br>What Weapons to Use: Up till you get duel weild you should be safe with a PGT.  Then once you get duel weild (lvl 17) get something like a crystalized sword and icetooth's claws or if youre short on cash mix one of those 2 mentioned with a crystallized blade.  Once you hit 25-30 start practicing piercing and 1hb with any weapon you can find.  Then in your early to mid 30s start investing for a SSoY (short sword of the ykesha) or 2, and since bards have pretty high dex it'll proc a lot.  My bard isn't high enough to help you out past like lvl 40.<br><br>What Armor to Get:  Try to get every peice of lambent you can asap, then go to frontier mountains and wait for Varsythnx (or whatever that sarnak's name is) to spawn and ask to loot his "Sleeves of the Ancient" they have stats better than plane armor =)  After that go to the planes and get some Imbrued Platemail and some Singing Steel<br><br>Where to Fight:<br>1-5: outside your city in that designated area.<br>5-11: Crushbone or Blackburrow<br>11-15:Dervs in Nro<br>15-18: Orcs in oasis<br>18-28: Gnolls and aviaks in south karana<br>28-32: Giants in frontier mountains<br>32-40: The overthere (the best exp but the crappiest loot)<br>40-50: Dreadlands or lower guk<br>50-55: Karnors<br>55+: Sebillis or something :)<br><br>From your bard friend on Prexus a (currently) lvl 35 bard and a proud member of Justice League.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
